Mailman:
========

Variables:

You can set the following variables per class to specify some defaults.

All are required, but can be configured by hiera.

$password:
------------------

sitewide password, which also be used on lists without a password set.

$admin:
---------------

Sitewide and default admin for lists.

$webserver:
-------------------

Default webserver for lists

$mailserver:
--------------------

Default mailserver for lists
